@NODE MAIN "FreeMouse V1.0  -  © 1998,1999 Alastair M. Robinson"

  @{b}A little tool to fine-tune your mouse@{ub}

  Copyright © 1998,1999  by  Alastair M. Robinson

Is your mouse too slow or too fast?

Have you tried a mouse-speeder, but found that the control isn't fine enough?

Are you sick of trawling through prefs directories to slow down the
mouse every time your kids use the computer?

Have you ever wished you could make your mouse @{B}just 20% faster?@{ub}

If this sounds like you, then you'll love FreeMouse!


FreeMouse provides continuous adjustment of mouse speed,
between 38% and 300%, via a hotkey-accessible GUI.


